# pestart configuration
# Lines:  app|Name|Path        - program shortcut
#         tile|Name|Path        - program shown as a live tile (also launches)
#         folder|Name|Path      - folder shortcut
#         name|Username         - override user display name
#         accent|R,G,B          - accent color
#
# A pestart.cfg placed next to pestart.exe overrides the built-in defaults.
# If this file is absent, pestart falls back to its built-in app list.

tile|BootICE|    X:\apps\bootice\BOOTICE.exe
tile|DiskGenius| X:\apps\diskgenius\DiskGenius.exe
tile|Ghost|      X:\apps\ghost\GHOST.exe
tile|HWiNFO|     X:\apps\hwinfo\HWiNFO.exe
tile|WinNTSetup| X:\apps\winntsetup\WinNTSetup_x64.exe

folder|System (X:)|   X:\
folder|Applications|   X:\apps
folder|Program Files|  X:\Program Files

name|WinPE User
accent|0,120,215
